{"tid":202790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強國冇咩】美國進口老鼠屎 究竟用嚟做乜？","createTime":"2017-04-15T18:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T17:05:22.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a692e47fbe5dba29ae5ce69f01c5d090889c9ca9","tid":202790,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170415/large/1492244410_2e6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170415%2Flarge%2F1492244410_2e6f.jpg&h=a76ddc0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n河南出入境檢驗檢疫局機場職員，周三從進境快件中截獲一批寄自美國的老鼠糞便，共6袋0.5千克。這是河南省首次截獲老鼠糞便，在全國口岸尚屬罕見。<br />\n<br />\n入境的老鼠糞便究竟有甚麼用途？河南出入境檢驗檢疫局有關人士指，對方聲稱「科研用」。因進口單位不能提供相關的檢疫許可證和檢疫證書，河南檢驗檢疫局依法對該批貨物實施扣留並進行後續處理。<br />\n老鼠糞便極易攜帶大量的病毒、細菌，可能傳播如鼠疫、地方性斑疹傷寒、流行性出血熱、鉤端螺旋體病等許多疾病，嚴重危害人類的健康，甚至對生命造成直接威脅，同時還會對生態環境、農林業生產安全帶來重大威脅和影響。根據相關規定，老鼠糞便屬於禁止進境的動物源性廢棄物。<br />\n新華社  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170415/56568741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170415%2F56568741&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoVy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=85dc12fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170415%2F56568741&h=2944f059\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170415/56568741</a>"},{"pid":"eb0c5de8619774ce53044c81d13a97dddc432698","tid":202790,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef168241dfaaae90e4b952b9b34c12ca60354327","tid":202790,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482494ddad0f7e7f3cb1ff3c05c03adc22b62647","tid":202790,"uid":574